          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-secondary">Marketing Opt-out</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
            <li>Unsubscribe from marketing emails at any time</li>
            <li>Opt-out of promotional communications</li>
          </ul>
