        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-secondary">8. Data Retention and Account Deletion</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-secondary">Active Accounts</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">We retain personal information for active accounts as long as necessary to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
            <li>Provide our services to you</li>
            <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
            <li>Resolve disputes</li>
            <li>Enforce our agreements</li>
          </ul>

