          <p class="mb-4">When you delete your account:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
            <li><strong>Immediate anonymization:</strong> Your personal information (name, email, phone, address) is immediately replaced with "Deleted User" identifiers</li>
            <li><strong>Order history preservation:</strong> Order records, payment amounts, and service dates are retained for business and tax compliance but anonymized</li>
            <li><strong>Legal compliance:</strong> We maintain anonymized transaction records for 7 years as required by business and tax law</li>
            <li><strong>No recovery:</strong> Deleted accounts cannot be restored - this action is permanent</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-secondary">Business Records</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Even after account deletion, we retain anonymized business records including:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
            <li>Order transaction amounts and dates (for tax and accounting purposes)</li>
            <li>Service completion records (for warranty and business analytics)</li>
            <li>Terms of service agreement timestamps (for legal protection)</li>
            <li>Payment processing records (required by financial regulations)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-base-content/70">
            <em>These records contain no personal identifying information after account deletion.</em>
          </p>
        </section>

